    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine<strong> </strong>your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>in a bowl with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> salad dressing</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) thinly</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced apple</strong> to the salad dressing and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed apple</strong></p>",
